{
  "stem": "1061.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whether we were actually on the death march on the 19th or 17th or 16th or 18th, I could not tell you.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I would place it as the first half of January 1945.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were told to just line up again and with-- got into a larger unit of women.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went always with women, you know-- never, never with men.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we-- this is January.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's bitter winter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Snow is falling.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We're lining up to go we don't know where.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this was also another part-- you know, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the fear-- you see, that fear that has somehow subsided.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Not-- you know, we were now indoors, working indoors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we thought, oh gee, maybe we will survive the war after all.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So it isn't that we weren't fearful, but we-- we-- we managed to live with the little fear that was left-- not little, but that fear that was already manageable.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, this was a brand new experience with it-- absolutely no idea what this was about.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "While we were in Auschwitz, we already saw that they were sort of liquidating it, because while we were there, there was still one chimney smoking-- and the smell of it.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the-- and the-- the fire, you could see it at night, and-- and we knew that people were being burned.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we knew that the-- the gypsies were killed off.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we heard of the Hungarian transports going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We heard of that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were trying to accommodate our orientation to what's happening-- that maybe something is really happening that's good, that-- that is maybe going to liberate us one way or another.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then we found ourselves on that road, on the death march, which was, of course, just the next step.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because as the Russian offensive was now coming closer-- as they sent us away from Starachowice camp when the Russian offensive started all the way out East-- now the Russians were much closer.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So now they were evacuating these camps, meaning all these camps that were in western Poland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Auschwitz was, you know, in western Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And on--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
